<TEXT>
<P>
(By Pei Shanqin)
</P>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, January 21 (Xinhua) -- The Tanzania Posts
Corporation (TPC) will this year print a special commemorative
stamp on the MV Bukoba disaster which killed more than 700 people
in May last year.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at a press conference here today, TPC Postermaster
General Suleiman Msofe said that the stamp will be printed under
"Marine Disaster" theme specifically for reminding the marine
authorities on the importance to observe passengers security
regulations and marine vessels.
</P>
