fled the scene after the explosion, the latest in a series of
attacks in the past week on abortion clinics in Tulsa, Oklahoma and
Atlanta.
</P>
<P>
The explosion happened on the 24th anniversary of a Supreme
Court ruling that legalized abortion nationwide. Anti-abortion
groups have been fighting the 1973 Supreme Court ruling and
demonstrators were gathering in Washington today for the annual march
protesting the 1973 decision. 
