majority in line with most of the majorities we have
secured in recent months.
</P>
<P>
"It shows once again that Labor cannot bring all their
people in, as we won the vote without any help from the
opposition parties," the source added.
</P>
<P>
However, while Major has reiterated his determination to hold
out until his favored election date of May l, senior Tories
acknowledge Commons arithmetic is making this more difficult by
the day. 
