<P>
The spokesman added that the Defense Headquarters has set up
another task force to patrol the Nigeria-Chad border to check the
infiltration of Chadian rebels.
</P>
<P>
He claimed intelligence reports indicated that the rebels
attempted to invade into Nigerian border towns and villages.
