and Marc Degryse.
</P>
<P>
PSV is recognized by many as the nurture grounds for great
football talents. Its former striker, Brazilian Ronaldo was on
Monday named by the sport's world governing body International
Football Federation (FIFA) as World Player of The Year 1996.
</P>
<P>
Founded in 1913, the PSV Eindhoven team has won the Dutch
League championship for 13 times, the Dutch Cup for seven times,
the UEFA Cup in 1978 and the European Champions' Cup in 1988.
</P>
