<HEADLINE> Malaysia Wins Japanese, U.S. Firms' Support for </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, January 22 (Xinhua) -- Malaysian Prime Minister
Mahathir Mohamad returned here this morning after his 10-day
