</P>
<P>
His visit since January 12, specially for promoting Malaysia's
Multimedia Super Corridor (MSC), succeeded in wooing U.S. and
Japanese companies to invest in the MSC, a 50km-by-15km zone
running south from the Kuala Lumpur City Center (KLCC).
</P>
