<HEADLINE> Shanghai Hosts International Children's Arts Festival </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, January 22 (Xinhua) -- Thousands of pigeons were
released into sky Monday in both Shanghai and Hong Kong, marking
the opening of the '97 International Children's Arts Festival of
Shanghai.
</P>
<P>
The theme of the festival is "Peace, Friendship and Future."
</P>
<P>
