<HEADLINE> Cameraman not to Pursue Charge against Rodman </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, January 21 (Xinhua) -- Eugene Amos, kicked by
Dennis Rodman during a basketball match, won't pursue charge
against Rodman, it was reported on Tuesday.
</P>
